8.commit_message: Bug 1511811 - Remove useless GECKO_BORROWED_TYPE_MUT.  This causes a typedef mozilla::ServoElementSnapshot ServoElementSnapshot; to be created, which we rely on bindgen not generating.  But bindgen will start (correctly) generating it in:    https://github.com/rust-lang/rust-bindgen/pull/1436  So easiest fix is just to remove this typedef, since it's just used by one FFI function.
